# UI Black-Only Guidelines

## Purpose
- Enforce a strictly black-only UI with grayscale accents across all surfaces and components.
- Provide consistent, accessible, mobile-first UI/UX guidance for the project.

## Non-Negotiable Constraints (Black-Only Theme)
- Color usage must be monochrome: pure black base (#000000) with grayscale only (#111, #222 … #fff). No chromatic hues.
- Backgrounds: black (#000000) by default; surfaces may use very dark gray steps for elevation.
- Text: white (#FFFFFF) on black; use grayscale for secondary/tertiary text ensuring WCAG 2.1 AA contrast.
- States (hover, focus, active, disabled): use opacity, underline, border, shadow, or grayscale shifts—not color.
- Links and CTAs: remain white text; emphasize via weight, underline, size, or container borders. No colored accents.
- Icons/illustrations: monochrome SVGs; tint via white/grayscale only.

## Accessibility
- Follow WCAG guidelines; validate contrast for all text and UI states.
- Use semantic HTML and ARIA where appropriate.
- Provide alt text for images/non-text content.
- Ensure full keyboard navigability and visible focus styles (e.g., 2px white or light-gray focus ring with adequate contrast on black).
- Test with screen readers and high-contrast modes.

## Implementation Notes (Tailwind)
- Only use black/white/gray tokens; no chromatic utilities.
- Prefer opacity, borders, shadows, and spacing for emphasis; avoid color-based emphasis.
- Keep base page background black and primary text white.
- Override any third-party styles to enforce monochrome if needed.

## Tailwind Black Theme Template

Use this template to enforce a black-only (monochrome) design with Tailwind in PHP/native HTML projects.

### tailwind.config.js

```javascript
/** Strict black-only Tailwind theme (PHP/HTML/CSS/JS projects) */
module.exports = {
  content: [
    "./**/*.php",
    "./**/*.html",
    "./**/*.js"
  ],
  darkMode: "class", // optional; default UI is already black
  theme: {
    colors: {
      transparent: "transparent",
      current: "currentColor",
      black: "#000000",
      white: "#FFFFFF",
      gray: {
        50: "#FAFAFA",
        100: "#F5F5F5",
        200: "#E5E5E5",
        300: "#D4D4D4",
        400: "#A3A3A3",
        500: "#737373",
        600: "#525252",
        700: "#404040",
        800: "#262626",
        900: "#171717",
        950: "#0A0A0A"
      }
    },
    extend: {}
  },
  plugins: []
};
```

